{"tid":524340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寒潮持續明最低8℃ 下周回暖最高22℃","createTime":"2018-01-09T13:14:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T15:38:54.000Z","uid":84436,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c7f8f50cb73d0f531ee41ddf7ce4a9958d836b","tid":524340,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:14:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%92%E6%BD%AE%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E8-%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9E%E6%9A%96%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%9822-033300259.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25AF%2592%25E6%25BD%25AE%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25BA%258C%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%259C%2580%25E4%25BD%258E8-%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%259A%2596%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%25AB%259822-033300259.html&d=CLs%2FCSULAZ2phu0cgJ4cPcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=3f2b0a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%AF%92%E6%BD%AE%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E6%98%8E%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%8E8-%E4%B8%8B%E5%91%A8%E5%9B%9E%E6%9A%96%E6%9C%80%E9%AB%9822-033300259.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】本港天氣寒冷，市民需注意保暖。天文台指，強烈冬季季候風會在未來數天持續為華南帶來寒冷的天氣，預測明日最低氣溫8℃，最高亦只得13℃，多雲及乾燥，早晚寒冷，下午部分時間有陽光。而周四最低亦只有10℃，最高15℃。<br />\n<br />\n天文台指，隨著覆蓋廣東沿岸的雲帶逐漸轉薄，該區天色好轉。預料季候風會在下週初緩和，沿岸地區氣溫將會回升，預測周日起開始氣溫逐步回升，周日起數天氣溫介乎14至22℃。"},{"pid":"60ec720f3ec6cf54652890cceaf129de1dd97ef9","tid":524340,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"點解香港嘅冬天咁短，得果幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8da3a45f4f3684d2660cf3edefaa9407d506ad5","tid":524340,"uid":54517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"60ec720f3ec6cf54652890cceaf129de1dd97ef9","tid":524340,"uid":74171,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:17:45.000Z","msg":"點解香港嘅冬天咁短，得果幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T14:45:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji